      %a{:href => http://www.mashoutable.com} social media services
      and tools can help you in your personal or professional life?  Don’t know where to start?  Don’t be frightened by new mediums of marketing and social media - we can help you.  Mashoutable will help you save time while getting your message out quickly and easily to all of your followers or just a targeted few with our tools including,
