      %a{href => http://www.mashoutable.com/VideoBODesc.aspx} Video BLASTOUT
      and
	  %a{:href => "http://www.mashoutable.com/TopTrendDesc.aspx"} Top Trend SHOUTOUT.
      To learn more about Mashoutable and how our tools were born, see our
      %a{:href => "http://www.mashoutable.com/About.aspx"} About Mashoutable
      section.
      %br/
      Please fill out the fields below with any questions, comments or concerns regard what you can do with Mashoutable’s
      = succeed "." do
      %a{:href => " http://www.mashoutable.com/ "} social media tools
